# ⚡ Spark Agency — Digital Marketing Landing Page

A fully customized, responsive premium landing page built for a fictional digital marketing agency **Spark Agency** using HTML, CSS, Bootstrap 5, and AOS animations.

---

## 🔗 Live DemO

---https://spark-agency-project.netlify.app/

---

## ✨ Features
- Fully responsive design (mobile + tablet + desktop)
- Sticky dark navbar with hover glow effects
- Animated hero section with AOS fade-in effects
- Services section with hover card animations
- Portfolio grid with CSS hover overlay effect
- Testimonials carousel slider
- Newsletter signup with JavaScript validation
- Contact form with JavaScript validation
- Smooth scrolling between sections
- Footer with social media icons

---

## 🛠️ Built With
- HTML5 (Semantic structure)
- CSS3 (Custom animations + overlay effects)
- Bootstrap 5 (Grid + components + icons)
- AOS.js (Scroll animations)
- JavaScript (Form validation)
- Google Fonts (Montserrat + Poppins)

---

## 📁 Project Structure
  premium-landing-page/
├── index.html        → Main HTML file
├── style.css         → Custom CSS styles
├── images/           → Project images
└── README.md         → Project documentation

  ## 🎨 Sections Included
| Section | Description |
|---------|-------------|
| Navbar | Sticky dark navbar with glow hover |
| Hero | Full screen dark gradient + AOS animations |
| Services | 3 service cards with hover effects |
| Portfolio | 4 project cards with overlay on hover |
| Testimonials | Bootstrap carousel with client reviews |
| Newsletter | Email signup with JS validation |
| Contact | Contact form with JS validation |
| Footer | Social media links + copyright |

---

## ⚡ Animations Used
| Animation | Where |
|-----------|-------|
| `fade-up` | Hero text + headings |
| `fade-right` | Portfolio left cards |
| `fade-left` | Portfolio right cards |
| CSS hover overlay | Portfolio cards |
| CSS translateY | Service cards |
| Glow effect | Navbar links + brand |

---

## 📱 Responsive On
- ✅ Mobile (320px+)
- ✅ Tablet (768px+)
- ✅ Desktop (1024px+)

---

## 🧠 What I Learned
- Bootstrap 5 carousel and accordion
- CSS position absolute for overlay effects
- AOS.js scroll animations
- JavaScript form validation
- CSS hover transitions and glow effects
- Responsive grid layouts

